org.gradoop.common.storage.impl.hbase.api

Interface PersistentGraphHead

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EPGMAttributed, EPGMElement, EPGMGraphHead, EPGMIdentifiable, EPGMLabeled, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HBaseGraphHead

    public interface PersistentGraphHead
extends EPGMGraphHead
    Representation of vertex data on the storage level. We additionally store vertices and edges contained in the graph for faster graph retrieval.
